sequenceDiagram
    participant N1 as Node 1
    participant N2 as Node 2
    participant N3 as Node 3
    participant CS as Coordination Service

    Note over N1,CS: Election round starts (startup or leader failure)

    N1->>CS: PUT /election/node1 TTL=10s
    N2->>CS: PUT /election/node2 TTL=10s
    N3->>CS: PUT /election/node3 TTL=10s

    CS-->>N1: Election won - you are Leader
    CS-->>N2: Election lost - follow Node 1
    CS-->>N3: Election lost - follow Node 1

    Note over N1: Becomes Leader
    Note over N2,N3: Enter Follower state

    loop Every 5s (heartbeat)
        N1->>CS: RENEW /election/node1 TTL=10s
        CS-->>N1: Lease renewed
    end

    Note over N1: Node 1 crashes - heartbeat stops

    CS->>N2: LeadershipLost event (TTL expired)
    CS->>N3: LeadershipLost event (TTL expired)

    Note over N2,N3: New election round begins
    N2->>CS: PUT /election/node2 TTL=10s
    N3->>CS: PUT /election/node3 TTL=10s
    CS-->>N2: Election won - you are new Leader
    CS-->>N3: Election lost - follow Node 2
